<ITEM>CXLIX. Que&s;tion propos'd, concerning the Object of Geometry.</ITEM>
<ITEM><PB REF="22">Sect. CL. At fir&s;t View, we are apt to think Vi&s;ible Exten&s;ion the Object of Geometry.</ITEM>
